BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Indivisible Sonoma County April General Meeting
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260413T180000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260413T200000
UID:0dea7f2f21e59f88d82755ce44cd01ae@mobilize.us
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://mobilize-uploads-prod.s3.amazonaws.com/u
 ploads/event/Capitol%20cropped_20260320230559319502.jpg
DESCRIPTION:There are competitive primaries this year in two of the three 
 new congressional districts (CA-01 and CA-04) that fall within Sonoma Coun
 ty and Indivisible Sonoma County is working to endorse in each. As part of
  that effort\, we are reaching out to the four candidates and are hoping t
 o secure their participation in a candidate forum\, in person\, at our nex
 t general meeting. Following the meeting\, active Indivisible Sonoma Count
 y members* will be asked to take part in our endorsement vote. Stay tune
LOCATION:Finley Community Center: Santa Rosa Recreation & Parks\, 2060 W C
 ollege Ave\, Santa Rosa\, CA\, 95401
URL:https://www.mobilize.us/indivisiblesonomacounty/event/924951/
X-SOURCE:Indivisible Sonoma County (Mobilize)
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Indivisible Sonoma County Single-Payer Task Force
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260330T183000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260330T200000
UID:0ae4d475dbdc78c841620a86fb2dae0d@mobilize.us
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://mobilize-uploads-prod.s3.amazonaws.com/u
 ploads/event/Healthcaare%20for%20All%20Logo%20%281200%20x%20630%20px%29_20
 260311043741105535.png
DESCRIPTION:Building the fight for universal healthcare within Indivisible
  In recent After-Hours meetings\, many members of Indy Soco were motivated
  to engage in the movement for single-payer healthcare for all\, removing 
 financial barriers to that care. Work with us to articulate and fight for 
 a future that truly meets the health needs of the people and builds a stro
 nger multi-cultural democracy than we ever had before. For more informatio
 n\, contact us at healthcareforallsonoma@gmail.com. If we coordinate an
LOCATION:Virtual event
URL:https://www.mobilize.us/indivisiblesonomacounty/event/919163/
X-SOURCE:Indivisible Sonoma County (Mobilize)
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Fight Back With Friends! Monthly Call To Action
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260428T153000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260428T163000
UID:a0f628329d7590fde7be75e2c23bdfe0@mobilize.us
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://mobilize-uploads-prod.s3.amazonaws.com/u
 ploads/event/16x9_Empower%20General%20Promo%20%281%29_20250318191514002894
 .png
DESCRIPTION:Fight Back With Friends! is a national program designed to hel
 p you activate your community! Using the Empower app\, the powerful relati
 onal organizing app\, we’ll equip you with the tools to connect with fri
 ends\, family\, and neighbors who need YOUR voice to get civically engaged
 . Join us on the fourth Tuesday of every month for a one-hour training ses
 sion\, where we’ll onboard new participants and introduce fresh calls to
  action that make a real impact.
LOCATION:Virtual event
URL:https://www.mobilize.us/indivisible/event/765804/
X-SOURCE:Indivisible Sonoma County (Mobilize)
END:VEVENT
