BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:What's the Plan with Leah and Ezra
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260402T120000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260402T130000
UID:4069d65c491e03f127e9e80d410cf959@mobilize.us
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://mobilize-uploads-prod.s3.amazonaws.com/u
 ploads/event/1295500807_20251204145520679878.png
DESCRIPTION:The chaos out of the White House is meant to overwhelm us. Our
  antidote is community. Join Indivisible co-founders Leah Greenberg and Ez
 ra Levin every Thursday to break down the week’s biggest political stori
 es\, answer your questions\, and map out strategies for taking action. Thi
 s is people-powered politics in real time. Questions can be submitted via 
 the Q&A function during the live event. Real talk. Real people. Real actio
 n. That's the plan.
LOCATION:Virtual event
URL:https://www.mobilize.us/indivisible/event/874938/
X-SOURCE:Indivisible Sonoma County (Mobilize)
END:VEVENT
